FBIS3-16421 "drsov051_a_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-051 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Security Council Official Meets Nixon LD1503130994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1030 GMT 15 Mar 94 LD1503130994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Oleg Lobov, secretary of the Russian Federation Security Council, received former U.S. President Richard Nixon today. In the course of a frank conversation lasting an hour and a half there was discussion of topical problems relating to Russia's domestic politicial situation, support for Russia's reforms and ensuring international security and stability.
